{
  "stem": "8703.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's where the place where the Polish gover-- the Polish underground, the army Krajowa and the army [INAUDIBLE] had their place, and they were hiding over there in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's where they camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The man told me this after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything was fine, but one thing-- I had some kind of trouble with my foot from walking so much.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the mother of [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Markevich ?] and another three people, four people, they were behind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they came over there and they came to the Polish underground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they said, all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We escaped from the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We would like to join the Polish underground to fight the common enemy, the Nazi-- Nazi Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They thought, well, if they were ready to fight, that they will be accepted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were shot right away, one by one, by the Polish underground army Krajowa, [NON-ENGLISH], the initials of the army of Krajowa.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But the five people that they were behind-- they found out what happened, and they didn't even go any further.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's what he told me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I forgot his name, and I-- and he told me that what happened to the 60 people what--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--who escaped that time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--From Skarzysko-Kamienna in the end of 1944.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was 1944.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we-- they took us about the 13th or 14th of August, 1944. 15Th August, we were all-- they were a selection.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They called everybody in a selection, made whoever's healthy, good looking, one side, sick people on the other side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They-- they had quite a few people-- whoever was weak and didn't look well-- they took them that time to the-- to the firing squad and they killed them all.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
